web3 practical 1 docker 

1] from docker website , download docker for windows , them complete installation and open command prompt 

docker --version

docker run hello-world

--------------------

if that doesn't work 

ping google.com

nslookup registry-1.docker.io

docker run hello-world
---------------------

output: hello from docker!

2] windows subsystem for Linux 


wsl --install

wsl --list --verbose

in ubuntu 

3] install curl 

sudo apt install curl git jq apt-transport-https -y


4] install golang 


sudo apt install golang-go -y

go version


5]install nodejs 

curl -fsSL https://deb.nodesource.com/setup_16.x | sudo -E bash -
sudo apt install -y nodejs

node -v
npm -v


6] install Hyperledger fabric 

mkdir -p ~/fabric && cd ~/fabric
curl -sSL https://bit.ly/2ysbOFE | bash -s

cd fabric-samples
ls

cd fabric-samples/test-network
./network.sh up createChannel -ca

./network.sh down

